6.4 What are your strengths and weaknesses as an offensive security professional?

### ðŸ’ª **Strengths**

| Strength                      | Description                                                                                                                                                                           |
| ----------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Analytical Thinking**       | I excel at breaking down complex systems to find hidden attack surfaces. I donâ€™t just look for known vulnerabilities; I think like an attacker and explore unexpected angles.         |
